<i>adverb</i>: 곰곰이 [곰ː고미], 곰곰 [곰ː곰] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>곰곰이 [곰ː고미]</dt><br>
<dd>pensively; musingly</dd><br>
<dd>여러 방면으로 깊이 생각하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of considering deeply from all aspects.</dd><br>
